verbose_text: CRF1 mRNA and CRF2 mRNA levels in DP-IBS and NDP-IBS patients were significantly higher than those in the control group (CRF1 : 0.070 +/- 0.004, 0.054 +/- 0.002, and 0.041 +/- 0.008, resp., F = 12.047, P < 0.01; CRF2 : 0.0031 +/- 0.0005, 0.0027 +/- 0.0004, and 0.0018 +/- 0.004, resp., F = 83.726, P < 0.01).
